$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: It's the fastest way to go from a great idea to a fully-launched, professional business. Your Kickstart package is an all-in-one service that includes a stunning website, professionally set up social media, foundational launch content, and the core strategy to tie it all together. We handle the execution so you can focus on your vision.

$control__SrVpnje9Y.value: What is THEEACE?" and "How does it work?

$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: THEEACE is your on-demand startup launch team. We provide an all-in-one "Kickstart" service for new entrepreneurs who need to look professional and launch, fast. Instead of you juggling multiple freelancers, we provide the website, branding, social media, and launch strategy in one simple package.

We offer transparent pricing to fit every founder's needs. Get your essential brand presence launched with our one-time Spark plan (₹2499). To actively grow with our popular Engine package including social media management, it's ₹7999/mo. For aggressive scaling, The Rocket plan (₹17,999/mo) provides a dedicated team and advanced growth tools.

$control__SrVpnje9Y.value: How long does it take to kickstart my business with you?

$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: Our goal is speed. While the exact timeline depends on the project, most Kickstart clients are fully launched with their new website and social media presence within 2-4 weeks from our initial strategy session.

$control__SrVpnje9Y.value: Do you provide custom digital marketing strategies?

$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: Yes, we tailor our digital marketing strategies to meet the unique needs and goals of each client. We conduct thorough research and analysis to create a customized plan that delivers optimal results.

$control__SrVpnje9Y.value: Are there any hidden costs? What about after the initial launch?

$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: We believe in 100% transparency. Our Kickstart package fee is a clear, upfront cost. The only other costs are for external services that you will own, like your domain name (~₹800/year) and website hosting. After your launch, you can take full control, or you can choose to continue with one of our monthly growth packages. You are always in control.

$control__SrVpnje9Y.value: I'm not a tech or marketing expert. Is that a problem?

$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: Not at all—that's why we exist. You bring the vision for your product or service; we bring the technical and marketing expertise. We explain everything in simple terms and handle all the complex work behind the scenes. Think of us as your instant tech co-founder.

$control__SrVpnje9Y.value: Do you work with founders outside of major cities like Mumbai or Delhi?

$control__nyAFEGVWc.value: Yes! We are a fully digital service and partner with founders from every corner of India. As long as you have a vision and an internet connection, we can help you launch a business that looks like it's headquartered in a major tech hub.
